{"tid":911791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【粉塵爆炸】生日會有學生玩潑麵粉 同學：用打火機燒乳頭都有","createTime":"2018-11-22T07:37:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T08:37:15.000Z","uid":75969,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e2ed3375fbfa8d63aa14d0b4cbdb87afdf1bb5a7","tid":911791,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T07:37:29.000Z","msg":"浸會大學凌晨時份發生粉塵爆炸事件﹝ <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Tup1Vb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Tup1Vb&d=WAA6jluBdfAnxImLkW4RQYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=aa5c5f8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Tup1Vb</a> ﹞，12人受傷。有同學指，除了玩麵粉，還有玩醬油包、雀粟包，甚至打火機燒乳頭，各式各樣。<br />\n<br />\n讀4年級的劉同學，今日如常上課。她認識其中一名受傷的一年級同學，據了解對方手受傷，留院治理中。<br />\n<br />\n劉同學指，她不清楚事發經過，不過以往活動，確有玩麵粉，以及不同類型的玩意，包括醬油包，就是「把蕃茄醬放在同學身上」，與及雀粟包，甚至用打火機燒男同學的乳頭。<br />\n<br />\n劉續說，並不是所有生日會或活動都會玩麵粉，「睇吓嗰層點玩，我嗰層只係食蛋糕，影吓相就完」。她指宿舍是不准點火。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181122/58943198\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181122%2F58943198&d=WAA6jluBdfAnxImLkW4RQYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=7bd76116\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181122%2F58943198&h=613eacc0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181122/58943198</a>"},{"pid":"950777b53a43cf6435d24441f739a1d59441b15a","tid":911791,"uid":117200,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T07:40:04.000Z","msg":"越爆越多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢間真係連中學都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f61496b1fd9e7bff7b7341c4dd859c44a3c779a6","tid":911791,"uid":171192,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T07:43:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>劉同學指，她不清楚事發經過，不過以往活動，確有玩麵粉，以及不同類型的玩意，包括醬油包，就是「把蕃茄醬放在同學身上」，與及雀粟包，甚至用打火機燒男同學的乳頭。</blockquote><br />\n男同學乳頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你玩埋我嗰份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05c80afadc2b6d297a7b77c2f1e866c8d556a1e3","tid":911791,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"f61496b1fd9e7bff7b7341c4dd859c44a3c779a6","tid":911791,"uid":171192,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T07:43:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>劉同學指，她不清楚事發經過，不過以往活動，確有玩麵粉，以及不同類型的玩意，包括醬油包，就是「把蕃茄醬放在同學身上」，與及雀粟包，甚至用打火機燒男同學的乳頭。</blockquote><br />\n男同學乳頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你玩埋我嗰份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T07:44:24.000Z","msg":"可以"},{"pid":"ff8687dd61beaf54f22967454927ddefd12c9c05","tid":911791,"uid":44083,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T07:44:41.000Z","msg":"燒到啲lin 黑哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d281bf297cfaea63eb73c2bd52cb4a1555f10f33","tid":911791,"uid":12458,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T07:47:42.000Z","msg":"我當年係hall最盡緊係燒閪毛同鳩毛 宜家進化成咁"},{"pid":"f5590e886270ce30fac5694713c5b72ee91f7c02","tid":911791,"uid":59898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T07:49:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 抵死"},{"pid":"d6233914a3161c6133f649f02591379d5b33744a","tid":911791,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":